ry Lucas did not sign with the team until 1963 when he tried to sign with the [[Cleveland Pipers]] of the [[American Basketball League (1961\u201363)|American Basketball League]] instead. He ended up sitting out the year when the deal fell through. His rookie season with the Royals began in the {{nbay|1963|app=season}}.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/history/players/lucasj_bio.html|title=Jerry Lucas Bio|accessdate=July 13, 2008|publisher=Turner Sports Interactive, Inc|work=NBA.com|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66W4H4Fvs?url=http://www.nba.com/history/players/lucasj_bio.html|archive-date=March 29, 2012|url-status=dead}}</ref>|group=lower-alpha|name=note_b}}\n| [[Forward (basketball)|Forward]]/[[Center (basketball)|Center]]\n| {{flagu|United States}}\n| [[Cincinnati Royals]]\n| {{sort|99|[[NBA territorial pick|T]]}}\n| [[1962 NBA draft|1962]]<ref group=lower-alpha name=note_b/>\n|-\n| {{nbay|1964}}\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"background-color:#FFFF99\"|{{sortname|Willis|Reed}}*\n| [[Center (basketball)|Center]]/[[Forward (basketball)|Forward]]\n| {{flagu|United States}}\n| [[New York Knicks]]\n| {{sort|08|8}}\n| [[1964 NBA draft|1964]]\n|-\n| {{nbay|1965}}\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"background-color:#FFFF99\"|{{sortname|Rick|Barry}}*\n| [[Forward (basketball)|Forward]]\n| {{flagu|United States}}\n| [[San Francisco Warriors]]\n| {{sort|02|2}}\n| [[1965 NBA draft|1965]]\n|-\n| {{nbay|1966}}\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"background-color:#FFFF99\"|{{sortname|Dave|Bing}}*\n| [[Guard (basketball)|Guard]]\n| {{flagu|United States}}\n| [[Detroit Pistons]]\n| {{sort|02|2}}\n| [[1966 NBA draft|1966]]\n|-\n| {{nbay|1967}}\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"background-color:#FFFF99\"|{{sortname|Earl|Monroe}}*\n| [[Guard (basketball)|Guard]]\n| {{flagu|United States}}\n| [[Baltimore Bullets (1963\u201373)|Baltimore Bullets]]\n| {{sort|02|2}}\n| [[1967 NBA draft|1967]]\n|-\n| {{nbay|1968}}\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"background-color:#FFFF99\"|{{sortname|Wes|Unseld}}*<ref group=lower-alpha n