rd]]\n| {{flagu|United States}}\n| [[Golden State Warriors]]\n| {{sort|11|11}}\n| [[1974 NBA draft|1974]]\n|-\n| {{nbay|1975}}\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\"| {{sortname|Alvan|Adams}}\n| [[Center (basketball)|Center]]/[[Forward (basketball)|Forward]]\n| {{flagu|United States}}\n| [[Phoenix Suns]]\n| {{sort|04|4}}\n| [[1975 NBA draft|1975]]\n|-\n| {{nbay|1976}}\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"background-color:#FFFF99\"|{{sortname|Adrian|Dantley}}*\n| [[Forward (basketball)|Forward]]/[[Guard (basketball)|Guard]]\n| {{flagu|United States}}\n| [[Buffalo Braves]]\n| {{sort|06|6}}\n| [[1976 NBA draft|1976]]\n|-\n| {{nbay|1977}}\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\"| {{sortname|Walter|Davis|dab=basketball}}\n| [[Guard (basketball)|Guard]]/[[Forward (basketball)|Forward]]\n| {{flagu|United States}}\n| [[Phoenix Suns]]\n| {{sort|05|5}}\n| [[1977 NBA draft|1977]]\n|-\n| {{nbay|1978}}\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\"| {{sortname|Phil|Ford|dab=basketball}}\n| [[Guard (basketball)|Guard]]\n| {{flagu|United States}}\n| [[Kansas City Kings]]\n| {{sort|02|2}}\n| [[1978 NBA draft|1978]]\n|-\n| {{nbay|1979}}\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"background-color:#FFFF99\"|{{sortname|Larry|Bird}}*{{#tag:ref|Though drafted in 1978 by the Boston Celtics, Larry Bird, opted to stay in college for his senior year, did not play in the NBA until 1979. His rookie season with the Celtics began in the {{nbay|1979|app=season}}.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/history/players/bird_bio.html|title=Larry Bird Bio|accessdate=July 13, 2008|publisher=Turner Sports Interactive, Inc|work=NBA.com}}</ref>|group=lower-alpha|name=note_d}}\n| [[Forward (basketball)|Forward]]\n| {{flagu|United States}}\n| [[Boston Celtics]]\n| {{sort|06|6}}\n| [[1978 NBA draft|1978]]<ref group=lower-alpha name=note_d/>\n|-\n| {{nbay|1980}}\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\"| {{sortname|Darrell|Griffith}}\n| [[Guard (basketball)|Guard]]\n| {{flagu|United Sta